<BaseLayout
  title="4-Layer PCB Engineering Consultation | Stackup Design & Impedance Control | XFPCB"
  description="XFPCB provides 4-layer PCB consultation and manufacturing with stackup architecture selection, impedance control methodology (50Ω, 90Ω diff, 100Ω diff), material selection (TG135/TG170/Rogers), thermal analysis, and DFM review for international buyers."
  keywords="4 layer PCB stackup, impedance control PCB, 4 layer PCB manufacturing, TG170 PCB, Rogers PCB, 50 ohm PCB, differential pair PCB, multilayer PCB design, China 4 layer PCB manufacturer, controlled impedance PCB"
  canonical="https://xfpcb.com/products/4-layer-pcb/"
  ogTitle="4-Layer PCB Engineering Consultation | Stackup Design & Impedance Control | XFPCB"
  ogDescription="XFPCB provides 4-layer PCB consultation and manufacturing with stackup architecture selection, impedance control methodology (50Ω, 90Ω diff, 100Ω diff), material selection (TG135/TG170/Rogers), thermal analysis, and DFM review for international buyers."
